{"tid":331281,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"長毛求救，幫唔幫？","createTime":"2017-07-22T04:44:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-22T04:55:12.000Z","uid":9997,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"10a92ad2f2bef2e424036717423ccffa7b4b616d","tid":331281,"uid":9997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T04:44:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/22/124443_19fbeaf28def15ff1df81eadf6b9377f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F22%2F124443_19fbeaf28def15ff1df81eadf6b9377f.jpg&h=2b21ee7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n🙏🙏🙏幫我哋一個忙，見到有長毛嘅banner就拆<br />\n<br />\n地政要求我哋7月24嘅前拆晒所有banner，否則要會逐條banner同我哋計清理費。新東選區好大，唔少banner仲要位於郊區，我哋實在唔夠時間清拆。我哋向地政提出過延期，可惜地政堅持唔可以改期。<br />\n<br />\n所以喺度懇請大家幫幫手拆banner🙏🙏🙏<br />\n<br />\nBanner位置和編號請見： <a href=\"http://Goo.gl/w48miY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoo.gl%2Fw48miY&d=%2Ftg94tjo1WDcL9EzSfBCB%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=d5c20557\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goo.gl/w48miY</a><br />\n<br />\n拆掉後請於本post留言告知位置和編號，謝謝。<br />\n<br />\n如果可以的話，請大家將拆咗嘅Banner帶回社民連總部（長沙灣永明街3號泰昌工廠大廈四樓B2室），我哋會回收再用。<br />\n<br />\n────────────<br />\n<br />\n為了讓社民連繼續抗爭，請立即以月捐方式，支持我們運作！<br />\n捐款支持社民連：<a href=\"http://www.lsd.org.hk/donate\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lsd.org.hk%2Fdonate&d=%2Ftg94tjo1WDcL9EzSfBCB%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=88649204\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.lsd.org.hk/donate</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/longhairhk/posts/10154985332318253:0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flonghairhk%2Fposts%2F10154985332318253%3A0&d=%2Ftg94tjo1WDcL9EzSfBCB%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=53e123e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/longhairhk/posts/10154985332318253:0</a>"},{"pid":"aab6db774737b10e51846f3f41d49f03eabaefe3","tid":331281,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"